Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/184684/', '', 'Rimegepant, Eptinezumab, Ubrogepant, Galcanezumab, Atogepant, Clonidine, Erenumab, Fremanezumab', 'Bupropion, Viloxazine, Esketamine', 1767369485);
